long_description: The compact Princeton Tec Fuel 4 LED headlamp uses 4 LEDs to blast a bright 43-lumen beam of light onto your backcountry adventures. Princeton Tec Fuel 4 Headlamp offers 3 brightness settings and a strobe function. LEDs throw a bright beam up to 35m on high, 28m on medium and 20m on low. Unique single-arm ratcheting head pivots up and down so you can aim the beam wherever you need it most. Large push-button switch is easily operated while wearing gloves. 3 AAA batteries, included, provide up to 50 hrs. of runtime on high, 90 hrs. on medium and 146 hrs. on low. Overstock.
